OL,3,CBody parts murder suspect told police
OL,4,C'it's a mistake' when arrested
OL,6,FA man arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,7,Fafter allegedly cutting his victim
OL,8,Finto 27 pieces told police: "It's
OL,9,Fdefinitely a mistake, 100%," a court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, was held on
OL,13,F25 April 2024 following the discovery
OL,14,Fof a human torso at Kersal Dale nature
OL,15,Freserve in Salford on 4 April .
OL,17,FHe denies the murder of pensioner
OL,18,FStuart Everett, 67, who he lived with
OL,19,Fin Winton, Salford.
