OL,3,CBody parts murder suspect told police
OL,4,C'it's a mistake' when arrested
OL,6,FThe human remains were initially
OL,7,Funidentified but police discovered
OL,8,FCCTV of a man going to the "deposition
OL,9,Fsite" with a heavy bag and returning
OL,10,Fwithout it, Manchester Crown Court was
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,FThree weeks after the grim discovery,
OL,14,Ftwo plain-clothed officers working on
OL,15,Fthe inquiry were driving an unmarked
OL,16,Fpolice car down the road in Salford
OL,17,Fand passed Majerkiewicz walking in the
OL,18,Fother direction, Manchester Crown
OL,19,FCourt heard.
