OL,3,CBody parts murder suspect told police
OL,4,C'it's a mistake' when arrested
OL,6,FThe Investigation Support Officer
OL,7,F(ISO), Clare Daly, told her colleague
OL,8,FISO Matthew Ross, behind the wheel: "I
OL,9,Fthink that's the suspect.
OL,11,F"I saw an individual on the pathway
OL,12,Fwho matched the description of the
OL,13,Fsuspect we were trying to trace," she
OL,14,Fsaid in a statement, read to the jury.
OL,16,FThe officers turned the car around and
OL,17,Ffollowed the suspect on foot before he
OL,18,Fgot on a number 100 bus, the court
OL,19,Fheard.
