OL,3,CBody parts murder suspect told police
OL,4,C'it's a mistake' when arrested
OL,6,FShortly afterwards, PC Paul Ashworth
OL,7,Fpulled his police car in front of the
OL,8,Fbus and boarded.
OL,10,FBody-worn video footage played to the
OL,11,Fjury showed the officer telling the
OL,12,Fsuspect he was being detained to be
OL,13,Fsearched, before he was handcuffed and
OL,14,Ftaken off the bus.
OL,16,FMajerkiewicz was told he had been
OL,17,Fidentified as a "person of interest"
OL,18,Fin a police investigation.
OL,20,FHe replied: "It's definitely a
OL,21,Fmistake, 100%."
