OL,6,FPC Ashworth then tells Majerkiewicz he
OL,7,Fhas been seen on several occasions on
OL,8,FCCTV by police investigating a serious
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FMajerkiewicz later says: "Someone
OL,12,Fsteal something?"
OL,14,FPC Ashworth replies: "It's a bit more
OL,15,Fserious than that, matey."
OL,17,FPolice found Majerkiewicz had the
OL,18,Fphone and bank cards belonging to Mr
OL,19,FEverett.
