OL,3,CBody parts murder suspect told police
OL,4,C'it's a mistake' when arrested
OL,6,FMinutes later, the officer then
OL,7,Fcautions Majerkiewicz, warning he is
OL,8,Fbeing arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,10,F"What?" the suspect replies, before
OL,11,Fasking for a translator and shaking
OL,12,Fhis head.
OL,14,FWhen police went to the house
OL,15,FMajerkiewicz shared with Mr Everett on
OL,16,FWorsley Road in Winton, they found a
OL,17,Fskip outside full of household items.
