OL,3,CBody parts murder suspect told police
OL,4,C'it's a mistake' when arrested
OL,6,FInside they found evidence of blood
OL,7,Fstaining and a clean-up operation,
OL,8,Fshowing "something terrible had
OL,9,Fhappened in that house", Jason Pitter
OL,10,FKC, prosecuting, told jurors.
OL,12,FAnalysis of Majerkiewicz's phone
OL,13,Fmovements and CCTV footage showed him
OL,14,Fcarrying bags and taking the bus on
OL,15,Fnumerous "deposition journeys" to get
OL,16,Frid of his victim's body, it is
OL,17,Falleged.
OL,19,FJurors were told only around one third
OL,20,Fof Mr Everett's body has been
OL,21,Frecovered.
