OL,3,CBody parts murder suspect told police
OL,4,C'it's a mistake' when arrested
OL,6,FPathology of the skull fragments
OL,7,Fshowed Mr Everett, a former civil
OL,8,Fservant originally from Derby, had
OL,9,Fbeen subject to a "sustained, severe
OL,10,Fblunt force physical assault", with
OL,11,Frepeated blows to his head, shattering
OL,12,Fand fracturing his skull, before being
OL,13,Fdismembered with a hacksaw.
OL,15,FMajerkiewicz denies the murder or
OL,16,Fmanslaughter of Mr Everett at their
OL,17,Fhouse in Winton, Salford, overnight
OL,18,Fbetween 27 March and 28 March, last
OL,19,Fyear.
OL,21,FThe trial continues.
